    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Toy Battlegrounds 是一款生存射击游戏，设定在儿童房间。与无尽的玩具波浪作战，使用各种武器，收集强化道具，面对不同类型的敌人，并在这场充满动作的玩具战争中证明你的技能！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261890/extras/17a6053dc31559ac4c7c047bc83bfdd3.poster.avif?t=1772360804\" width=604 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261890/extras/17a6053dc31559ac4c7c047bc83bfdd3.webm?t=1772360804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261890/extras/17a6053dc31559ac4c7c047bc83bfdd3.mp4?t=1772360804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Toy Battlegrounds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Toy Battlegrounds 是一款生存射击游戏，设定在一个充满活力且混乱的儿童房间。你被缩小到玩具大小，必须在夜深人静时生存下去，抵挡一波又一波的活跃玩具。使用多种武器并解锁强化道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261890/extras/5e0a8075acadf627658d7919b34c364e.poster.avif?t=1772360804\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261890/extras/5e0a8075acadf627658d7919b34c364e.webm?t=1772360804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261890/extras/5e0a8075acadf627658d7919b34c364e.mp4?t=1772360804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与不同类型的敌人作战，从成群的玩具士兵到巨大的BOSS，穿越房间中的障碍物。游戏设有夜晚的氛围，紧张的游戏过程和不断的行动，Toy Battlegrounds 挑战你坚守阵地，成为玩具世界的终极英雄！</p>",
